Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with stereo camera calibration and image processing.
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper specifically mentions autonomous vehicles and the need for real-time calibration.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possibility as the paper uses optimization techniques to recover calibration parameters.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a possibility as the paper uses an objective function to maximize the number of successfully recovered depth pixels.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with the calibration of a system (stereo camera setup) in the context of autonomous vehicles.
